extendedInfo.description: Listen to and connect with Big 99.9 Coyote Country on your Phone.The Big 99.9 Coyote Country is KXLY-FM, your home for Jay & Kevin and BIG Country Music!  You'll hear Brad Paisley, Lady Antebellum, The Zac Brown Band, Miranda Lambert, Rascal Flatts, Kenny Chesney, and more of today's BIGGEST stars!  The BIG 99.9 Coyote Country is perfect at home, at work, or wherever you want the BIGGEST Country Music!
